com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.data

Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.data.BaseData<TypeInfo<?>>
      • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.data.MapData

  • public class MapData
extends BaseData<TypeInfo<?>>
    A map data, MapData can hold parent elements, MapData that hold parent element is called 'Child MapData'. The purpose of this class is to hold information to be retrieved later by another context. MapData hold a Map with MapData as key and a LIFO list as value.
